 (1) Lun7 iong2-seng5 thoan5-to7-chia2 e5 su7-giap8. Chit hang7 su7-giap8 tui3 thoan5 to7-li2 chit hong-bin7 lai5 khoaN3 si7 boe7 bian2 bo5 tit e5. In-ui7 goa7-kok lang5 tu2-tu2 lai5 Tai5-oan5 e5 si5 u7 chiong2-chiong2 e5 khun3-lan5, chhin-chhiuN7 pun2-toe7 e5 jin5-cheng5, hong-siok8 e5 bo5 koan3-si3, iah8 thiN-khi3 chui2-thou2 e5 bo5 hap8, khah siong5 ai3 phoa3-piN7, sou2-i2 na7-si7 pun2-toe7 lang5 chu7-jian5 khah m7 bian2 kiaN chiah-e5 su7. Koh goa7-kok lang5 sui-bong2 koh khah thong-tat8 pun2-toe7 oe7, iah8 si7 m7-tat8-tioh8 pun2-toe7 lang5 e5 chu7-iu5 chu7-chai7. Kai Bok8-su u7 chhim-chhim siuN7 kau3 chia, sou2-i2 tek-khak tioh8 seng kau3-iok8 pun2-toe7 lang5, hou7 in chiah lai5 thoan5 to7-li2 khah u7 kong-hau7, in-ui7 in khah chai-iaN2 tang5-chok8 e5 seng3-chit kap sia7-hoe7 seng-oah8 e5 chong7-thai7, sou2-i2 khah chai-iaN2 thang eng7 tek-tong e5 hoat-tou7 lai5 chi2-to7 ka3-si7 tong5-pau. 
