 Lun7 sou2 teh ka3 e5 kho-bok8, Seng3-keng i2-goa7 iau2 u7 chhin-chhiuN7 Lek8-su2, Te7-li2, Tong7-but8-hak8, Sit8-but8-hak8, Khong3-but8-hak8, Te7-chit-hak8, Sou3-hak8, Thian-bun5-hak8 teng2-teng2 e5 ko-teng2 phou2-thong e5 hak8-kho3. Jit8-si5 thak8-chheh, am3-si5 chu7-hoe7 ti7 toa7 kang2-tng5. Ti7 chit-e5 chip8-hoe7 u7 lu2 hak8-seng, su-lip8 e5 sio2 hak8-seng kap it-poaN e5 sin3-chia2, chham Li2-hak8-tong5 Tai7-chu-iN7 e5 lam5 hak8-seng. Tak8-am3 tui3 poeh-tiam2 khi2, cheng3-lang5 chiu7 long2 chiau5-kau3, lu2 hak8-seng che7 tiong-ng, lam5 hak8-seng che7 ti7 au7-bin7 kap siang-peng5-piN e5 sou2-chai7, sio2 hak8-seng che7 ti7 lu2 hak8-seng e5 bin7-cheng5, i2-goa7 e5 sin3-chia2 long2 che7 ti7 te7-it au7-bin7, che7 liau2-au7 chiu7 gim5-si, ki5-to2, khui-hoe7, au7-lai5 chiu7 tho2-lun7 kap ian2-soat teng2-teng2, che long2 si7 lam5-lu2 hak8-seng teh choe3, ian2-soat si7 gou7-hun kan na7-tiaN7, lun7 gian5-gu2, the2-thai3, ku2-tong7 teng2-teng2, na7 u7 bo5 tu2-ho2 e5 sou2-chai7, bo5 lun7 sim2-mih8 lang5 sui5-pian7 thang khi2-lai5 kong2, khi2-thau5 kong2 e5 lang5 khoaN3-kiN3 hiah-nih8 choe7 e5 theng3-chiong3 chin kiaN, bo5 poaN3 ku3 oe7 thang kong2, m7-ku2 an2-ni thoan3-lian7 kau3 chit8 geh8 goa7 jit8 liau2, chiu7 tak8-lang5 ian2-soat put-chi2 u7 khah chu7-jian5. Koh u7 si5 iah8 u7 khui pian7-lun7-hoe7 kap chio3 iaN2-teng hou7 in khoaN3. 
