 Kai Bok8-su khoaN3 hu7-jin5-lang5 chit khoan2 e5 keng2-gu7, i put-chi2 thoe3 in kho2-lin5, sou2-i2 ti3-i3 iong2-seng5 lu2 thoan5-to7, sou2-i2 au7-lai5 u7 siat Lu2-hak8-tong5. Hit-si5 e5 Lu2-hak8-tong5 khiok kap hian7-si5 e5 che3-tou7 bo5 siang5, hit lai7-bin7 kau3-iok8 e5 hong-hoat, kap hian7-si5 e5 Lu2-oh8 u7 koh-iuN7, in-ui7 ti7 hit tiong-kan m7-na7 u7 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 teh thak8, koh iah8 u7 toa7-han3 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5, chhin-chhiuN7 thoan5-to7-niu5, a2-si7 bok8-su-niu5, u7-e5 iah8-si7 u7 saN-kap ti7-teh thak8. Teh ka3 e5 lang5, u7 ta-pou sian-siN, koh u7 cha-bou2 sian-siN. Sou2 ka3 e5 kho-bok8, u7 thak8-chheh, sip8-ji7, chhiuN3-koa, Seng3-chheh, lek8-su2, te7-li2, kap bun7-tap teng2-teng2. Na7 keng-ke3 chiah-e5 kho3-theng5 lai5 chut-giap8 e5, chiu7 thang choe3 lu2 thoan5-to7, thang siu7 phai3 khi3 si3-koe3 thoan5 to7-li2 hou7 hu7-jin5-lang5 thiaN. Sou2-i2 lun7 kau3-hoe7 e5 hoat-tat8, chit8-pou7-hun7 si7 tui3 lu2-chu2 tau3 thoan5 to7-li2 e5 ti3-im3. 
